3. Decide+validate retry helper ŌĆö `lib/src/loop_driver/validation_retry.dart`

   Two independent retry budgets per PRD ┬¦17:
   - **Schema budget = 1**. On `SchemaRejection`, retry once with the schema error appended as a `system` `PromptMessage`. Second `SchemaRejection` ŌåÆ throw `SchemaExhausted(cause)`.
   - **Validator budget = 3**. On `ActionValidator` reject, splice `{tool, reason, expected, got}` JSON as a `system` message into the next attempt's prompt. After 3 rejects ŌåÆ throw `InvalidActionExhausted(rejections)`.

   ```dart
   class ValidationLoopResult {
     final ModelDecision decision; final int retries;
     final List<String> rejections;
     const ValidationLoopResult(this.decision, this.retries, this.rejections);
   }
   class InvalidActionExhausted implements Exception { final List<String> rejections;
     const InvalidActionExhausted(this.rejections); }
   class SchemaExhausted implements Exception { final SchemaRejection cause;
     const SchemaExhausted(this.cause); }

   Future<ValidationLoopResult> decideAndValidate({
     required ModelProvider provider, required PromptPayload basePrompt,
     required ActionSchema schema, required ActionValidator validator,
     required Observation observation, required List<ToolDescriptor> mergedTools,
     int maxValidationRetries = 3,
   });
   ```

