## Approach
`ModelProvider` + `ActionSchema` in `exploration_agent`. Schema recomposed every turn (PRD ┬¦16.2): `action` is a `oneOf` over each tool's name + `inputSchema`. Schema-violating output throws `SchemaRejection`; loop driver (.18) retries once per PRD ┬¦17. Web-compatible: pure Dart, `package:json_schema` draft-07. Also defines `PromptPayload` and `ToolDescriptor` (consumed here; produced by .13/.12) since .14 lands earlier in build order. Depends on .11; blocks .15/.16.

