## Implementation Plan

1. **Add `SemanticsCapture.lookup` (additive, cx6.5 file)** ŌĆö `packages/exploration_flutter/lib/src/semantics/semantics_capture.dart`

   The existing `_stableIds` map records `frameworkNodeId ŌåÆ stableId`. Invert it and re-walk the live tree to return the matching `SemanticsNode`.

   ```dart
   /// Returns the live SemanticsNode whose stable id is [stableId], or
   /// null if no such node was captured this session OR the node was
   /// disposed since capture. Adds no caching ŌĆö re-walks the live tree
   /// each call (cheap; capture itself walks too).
   SemanticsNode? lookup(int stableId) {
     final int? fwkId = _stableIds.entries
         .firstWhere((e) => e.value == stableId,
                     orElse: () => const MapEntry(-1, -1)).key;
     if (fwkId == -1) return null;
     return _findNodeById(fwkId);
   }
   SemanticsNode? _findNodeById(int fwkId) {
     SemanticsNode? out;
     void visit(SemanticsNode n) {
       if (out != null) return;
       if (n.id == fwkId) { out = n; return; }
       n.visitChildren((child) { visit(child); return out == null; });
     }
     final root = _findRootSemanticsNode();
     if (root != null) visit(root);
     return out;
   }
   ```

