## Approach
`ExplorationBinding extends WidgetsFlutterBinding` with `ensureInitialized({required List<ExplorationPlugin> plugins})`. Installs as singleton, hard-fails on foreign binding, no-ops outside debug/profile, registers `ext.flutter.exploration.core.handshake`. Registry deferred to cx6.3 ŌĆö this bead stores the plugin list verbatim. cx6.2 introduces a minimal `ExplorationPlugin` placeholder (`namespace` only); cx6.3 extends it additively (non-breaking per PRD ┬¦7.7). Anchors: PRD ┬¦6.1, ┬¦6.5, ┬¦7.6, ┬¦17, ┬¦22.

