3. **`ActionRing` with default capacity 5** ŌĆö `packages/exploration_agent/lib/src/memory/action_ring.dart` (new file)

   ```dart
   class ActionRing {
     ActionRing({this.capacity = 5}) : assert(capacity > 0);
     final int capacity;
     final List<String> _entries = <String>[];

     /// Most-recent-last, capped at [capacity].
     List<String> get entries => List<String>.unmodifiable(_entries);

     void push(String entry) {
       _entries.add(entry);
       if (_entries.length > capacity) {
         _entries.removeAt(0);
       }
     }
   }
   ```

